we'll find out all about you.

286
00:13:35,379 --> 00:13:38,448
What if we don't like
what we find?

287
00:13:38,517 --> 00:13:39,896
I can't imagine that.

288
00:13:39,965 --> 00:13:41,413
You know,
I haven't told you this before,

289
00:13:41,482 --> 00:13:42,620
but, somehow, I feel

290
00:13:42,689 --> 00:13:44,344
like there's
something different,

291
00:13:44,413 --> 00:13:47,517
but what if it turns out
that I have a really weird past?

292
00:13:47,586 --> 00:13:49,000
What if I did
something terrible,

293
00:13:49,068 --> 00:13:52,586
and that's why
I can't even remember who I am?

294
00:13:52,655 --> 00:13:56,551
Kristin,
I promise you, we won't.

295
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:59,310
There's no way that you could be
the person you are now

296
00:13:59,379 --> 00:14:01,724
and then to have been
something completely different

297
00:14:01,793 --> 00:14:02,965
before,

298
00:14:03,034 --> 00:14:05,551
and no matter what,

299
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:08,896
nothing will ever change
the way I feel about you.

300
00:14:08,965 --> 00:14:10,965
It's not going to happen.

301
00:14:14,448 --> 00:14:16,000
Is that my "yes"?

302
00:14:17,517 --> 00:14:18,862
Yes.

303
00:14:18,931 --> 00:14:20,206
Oh...

304
00:14:21,931 --> 00:14:24,551
We're going to get married,

305
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:26,379
and we're going to live
happily ever after.

306
00:14:26,448 --> 00:14:28,655
Just like in the fairy tales?

307
00:14:28,724 --> 00:14:30,206
Oh, yeah,

308
00:14:30,275 --> 00:14:31,862
just like in all the stories
of make-believe.

309
00:14:31,931 --> 00:14:33,137
Oh.

310
00:14:37,689 --> 00:14:39,896
If you want
driving lessons,

311
00:14:39,965 --> 00:14:41,379
I'll make them

312
00:14:41,448 --> 00:14:43,448
one of your
Christmas presents.

313
00:14:49,103 --> 00:14:51,551
Wow.

314
00:14:51,620 --> 00:14:54,689
We'd better go finish dessert
before uncle Johnny does.

315
00:14:54,758 --> 00:14:56,241
I heard that.

316
00:14:56,310 --> 00:14:57,862
Too late.

317
00:14:59,448 --> 00:15:00,931
We have find out, Kyle.

318
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,793
We have to help her.

319
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,379
Wahoo, are you in there?

320
00:15:13,448 --> 00:15:16,275
No. I'm not here.

321
00:15:16,344 --> 00:15:18,655
We have work to do.

322
00:15:18,724 --> 00:15:19,724
All the elves
that helped you out last time

