324
00:15:21,448 --> 00:15:22,931
No cookies for three months!

325
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,620
Do you know what I've suffered?

326
00:15:24,689 --> 00:15:26,586
Do you know
what I've been through?

327
00:15:26,655 --> 00:15:29,758
Making reindeer-poo pies?

328
00:15:29,827 --> 00:15:32,413
Close enough,

329
00:15:32,482 --> 00:15:34,758
