332
00:15:38,379 --> 00:15:40,620
I'll make it
worth your while.

333
00:15:40,689 --> 00:15:42,379
Get a hammer and a chisel
and come with me.

334
00:15:43,931 --> 00:15:46,413
All those years
of trying to get rid of her,

335
00:15:46,482 --> 00:15:48,379
and she did it on her own.

336
00:15:48,448 --> 00:15:50,344
She left of her own free will,

337
00:15:50,413 --> 00:15:52,586
